my daughter was already gone from the island.

587
00:34:41,400 --> 00:34:42,530
There's no mistake.

588
00:34:42,639 --> 00:34:44,320
She came back on the same boat with me.

589
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:45,199
As soon as we landed,

590
00:34:45,199 --> 00:34:47,000
she was taken away by the police.

591
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:48,800
Why would the police arrest her?

592
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:49,560
Well,

593
00:34:50,600 --> 00:34:51,880
it's definitely true.

594
00:34:52,199 --> 00:34:53,800
I need to get back to headquarters.

595
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:54,960
I can't stay long.

596
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:56,719
You'd better think of something quickly.

597
00:34:56,719 --> 00:34:57,640
Hurry!

598
00:34:59,120 --> 00:34:59,920
Please wait.

599
00:35:03,600 --> 00:35:05,520
Only Japanese people can come and go from this island.

600
00:35:05,520 --> 00:35:07,120
How could Ying'er come back?

601
00:35:07,440 --> 00:35:09,000
What do you think is going on?

602
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:10,320
I'm sure it's this guy

603
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:11,880
up to something with the Japanese.

604
00:35:11,880 --> 00:35:13,740
I'll go ask him what's happening.

605
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:16,740
Don't be so impulsive.

606
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:18,080
Take this.

607
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:19,640
I'll go check.

608
00:35:25,280 --> 00:35:26,680
Tell me the truth now.

609
00:35:27,600 --> 00:35:29,120
Your real name,

610
00:35:29,120 --> 00:35:30,080
occupation,

611
00:35:30,080 --> 00:35:31,440
and mission.

612
00:35:33,120 --> 00:35:34,520
Starting with your name,

613
00:35:34,920 --> 00:35:35,920
your full name,

614
00:35:36,280 --> 00:35:37,160
your position,

615
00:35:37,400 --> 00:35:38,440
and your mission.

616
00:35:47,200 --> 00:35:49,200
This bag belongs to you, doesn't it?

617
00:35:49,520 --> 00:35:51,640
This is your purse.

618
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:57,240
Guards!

619
00:35:57,240 --> 00:35:57,880
Yes.

620
00:35:58,520 --> 00:36:00,760
Have Shanghai investigate

621
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:03,280
ID number 4906,

622
00:36:03,280 --> 00:36:05,360
who got this woman

623
00:36:05,360 --> 00:36:06,760
this special island entry permit.

624
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:07,600
Yes.

625
00:36:14,800 --> 00:36:16,320
Is this your gun?

626
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:18,320
This is your gun.

627
00:36:25,800 --> 00:36:27,720
I won't ask a second time.

628
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:30,960
I'll tell you once more.

629
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:35,400
Are these your bag and gun?

630
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:37,880
This is your gun and your bag.

631
00:36:39,200 --> 00:36:41,000
How did you get to this island?

632
00:36:41,360 --> 00:36:43,840
And who gave you the special pass?

633
00:36:44,240 --> 00:36:45,370
How did you get here?

634
00:36:45,680 --> 00:36:46,120
The permit.

635
00:36:46,120 --> 00:36:48,250
First, find an ill-tempered officer.

636
00:36:48,320 --> 00:36:49,180
He will hit you.

637
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:50,140
Insult you.

638
00:36:50,240 --> 00:36:51,040
Threaten you.

639
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:54,020
Making you feel extreme psychological terror.

640
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:56,680
Your gun.

641
00:36:57,160 --> 00:36:58,080
Take it.

642
00:36:58,600 --> 00:36:59,840
Hold it properly.

643
00:37:00,520 --> 00:37:01,920
This gun is yours, right?

644
00:37:05,200 --> 00:37:07,720
This gun belongs to you, right?

645
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:10,440
This weapon is definitely yours.

646
00:37:10,640 --> 00:37:11,240
Hold on.

647
00:37:11,720 --> 00:37:13,120
Remember to stay silent.

648
00:37:13,480 --> 00:37:16,210
I arrived on the island only 5 hours after you did.

649
00:37:18,680 --> 00:37:19,280
Captain!

650
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:23,060
What are you doing?

651
00:37:23,320 --> 00:37:23,850
Captain,

652
00:37:24,360 --> 00:37:26,160
that woman is Mr. Ye's daughter.

653
00:37:29,200 --> 00:37:30,040
I see.

654
00:37:32,200 --> 00:37:35,160
So she's Mr. Ye's daughter.

655
00:37:35,160 --> 00:37:36,960
Not from this island.

656
00:37:38,120 --> 00:37:38,640
Yes.

657
00:37:39,280 --> 00:37:41,540
That old man and his servant are outside.

658
00:37:45,520 --> 00:37:47,560
Let's arrest him first

659
00:37:47,560 --> 00:37:48,640
and let Sasaki handle it.

660
00:37:48,640 --> 00:37:49,360
No need.

661
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:51,480
Call Sasaki over.

662
00:37:58,440 --> 00:37:59,320
Tell me now!

663
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:00,080
Captain.

664
00:38:11,120 --> 00:38:12,180
Here's our chance.

665
00:38:12,680 --> 00:38:15,000
Don't worry about things here.

666
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:16,360
Go to Ye Degong's house in Tanjiawan immediately.

667
00:38:16,360 --> 00:38:17,890
Dig out the secret chamber.

668
00:38:18,360 --> 00:38:18,890
Yes, sir.

669
00:38:31,160 --> 00:38:33,400
Move aside.

670
00:38:38,840 --> 00:38:39,640
Colonel.

671
00:38:41,240 --> 00:38:42,170
May I have a word?

672
00:38:48,960 --> 00:38:49,840
Look at this.

673
00:38:51,880 --> 00:38:53,600
Your female assistant has been arrested.

674
00:38:53,600 --> 00:38:56,520
It's a call from the Sanzao Island Special Police Unit.

675
00:38:56,520 --> 00:38:57,240
They seem to have discovered

676
00:38:57,240 --> 00:38:58,360
her special pass.

677
00:39:00,120 --> 00:39:01,920
Something must have gone wrong.

678
00:39:02,600 --> 00:39:03,520
Listen to me.

679
00:39:03,720 --> 00:39:05,250
The operation is canceled.

680
00:39:06,400 --> 00:39:07,320
Stay calm.

681
00:39:08,080 --> 00:39:09,280
You must remain calm.

682
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:10,880
It will be dangerous.

683
00:39:11,680 --> 00:39:13,010
What else did they find?

684
00:39:13,280 --> 00:39:14,410
Nothing else so far.

685
00:39:15,360 --> 00:39:16,090
Let me think.

686
00:39:18,440 --> 00:39:20,040
This telegram arriving here

687
00:39:20,120 --> 00:39:20,880
means she's been arrested

688
00:39:20,880 --> 00:39:22,210
for more than two hours.

689
00:39:22,680 --> 00:39:23,040
It will take me

690
00:39:23,040 --> 00:39:24,570
another two hours by plane.

691
00:39:31,680 --> 00:39:32,210
Let's go.

692
00:39:33,680 --> 00:39:34,240
No.

693
00:39:51,600 --> 00:39:52,680
Throughout the journey,

694
00:39:52,680 --> 00:39:54,200
Wu Mu was reviewing

695
00:39:54,200 --> 00:39:57,280
all his activities with Ye Biying in Shanghai.

696
00:39:57,680 --> 00:39:59,320
He went through every step

697
00:39:59,320 --> 00:40:01,840
of the island entry procedure with Ye Biying.

698
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:04,040
He examined every detail

699
00:40:04,040 --> 00:40:06,440
that might have exposed their identities.

700
00:40:06,640 --> 00:40:08,280
Wu Mu carefully reviewed

701
00:40:08,280 --> 00:40:10,200
all activities in Shanghai.

702
00:40:10,440 --> 00:40:12,360
From this, he concluded

703
00:40:12,360 --> 00:40:14,040
that Ye Biying's arrest

704
00:40:14,040 --> 00:40:15,680
must have been accidental.

705
00:40:16,000 --> 00:40:17,400
Let's go somewhere else.

706
00:41:02,160 --> 00:41:02,880
Captain.

707
00:41:03,280 --> 00:41:03,680
Yes.

708
00:41:04,680 --> 00:41:05,600
The special entry permit

709
00:41:05,600 --> 00:41:06,640
for Ye Biying's island access

710
00:41:06,640 --> 00:41:08,000
was issued by a colonel.

711
00:41:10,600 --> 00:41:11,880
The Shanghai Garrison Intelligence Section

712
00:41:11,880 --> 00:41:12,560
has already classified

713
00:41:12,560 --> 00:41:13,960
these documents as confidential.

714
00:41:13,960 --> 00:41:14,400
Therefore,

715
00:41:14,400 --> 00:41:17,040
a regular investigation won't yield results

716
00:41:17,040 --> 00:41:19,300
unless Commander Fujita signs off on it.

717
00:41:19,440 --> 00:41:22,040
What a hassle.

718
00:41:22,040 --> 00:41:23,880
That stubborn old man.

719
00:41:24,400 --> 00:41:25,600
What the hell?

720
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:27,240
We can use

721
00:41:27,360 --> 00:41:29,200
the father of that woman we just detained,

722
00:41:29,200 --> 00:41:31,400
but no torture.

723
00:41:51,120 --> 00:41:51,800
How's it going?

724
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:53,060
Too impulsive. Idiot.

725
00:41:54,080 --> 00:41:56,640
Did you see that woman's expression?

726
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:00,680
Look how she held her breath,

727
00:42:00,680 --> 00:42:02,400
she even stopped breathing.

728
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:04,490
What does that mean?

729
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:07,400
It's a primal human instinct.

730
00:42:07,400 --> 00:42:09,480
When trying to conceal or hide something,

731
00:42:09,480 --> 00:42:10,760
this is the reaction.

732
00:42:10,760 --> 00:42:12,200
When humans cannot fight back

733
00:42:12,200 --> 00:42:14,840
or resist,

734
00:42:14,840 --> 00:42:20,440
they try to hide.

735
00:42:20,480 --> 00:42:22,880
That's why she responded this way.

736
00:42:22,920 --> 00:42:23,960
In other words,

737
00:42:23,960 --> 00:42:25,880
she felt extreme pressure.

738
00:42:26,200 --> 00:42:27,720
Now we just wait for her.

739
00:42:27,720 --> 00:42:29,920
Your psychological defenses are crumbling.
